Sub-Task description: "Implement the complete set of HTML template files for the TravelPlanner web application, starting with creating 'dashboard.html' to resolve the TemplateNotFound error. Each template must strictly follow the page design specifications in the requirements document, including all specified elements with correct IDs, page titles, and layout. Templates should be created for all ten pages  Dashboard, Destinations, Destination Details, Itinerary Planning, Accommodations, Transportation, Travel Packages, Trip Management, Booking Confirmation, and Travel Recommendations. Coordinate with Programmer 1 to ensure templates match the data and variables passed from Flask routes."
